{"tid":2330933,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"★中央經濟工作會議：堅持房子是用來住的、不是用來炒的","createTime":"2020-12-18T11:21:44.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-20T05:17:23.000Z","uid":19454,"like":1,"dislike":10,"uniUserReply":22,"replies":[{"pid":"2b006999f4dc9a2a9f6ce1f5742f231aba359621","tid":2330933,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-18T11:21:44.000Z","msg":"中央經濟工作會議指出，解決好大城市住房突出問題。住房問題關係民生福祉。要堅持房子是用來住的、不是用來炒的定位，因地制宜、多策並舉，促進房地產市場平穩健康發展。<br />\n<br />\n《新華社》報道，會議強調，要堅持房子是用來住的、不是用來炒的定位，因地制宜、多策並舉，促進房地產市場平穩健康發展。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n會議還指出，要高度重視保障性租賃住房建設，加快完善長租房政策，逐步使租購住房在享受公共服務上具有同等權利，規範發展長租房市場<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.hk01.com/財經快訊/563655/中央經濟工作會議-要堅持房住不炒定位\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hk01.com%2F%E8%B2%A1%E7%B6%93%E5%BF%AB%E8%A8%8A%2F563655%2F%E4%B8%AD%E5%A4%AE%E7%B6%93%E6%BF%9F%E5%B7%A5%E4%BD%9C%E6%9C%83%E8%AD%B0-%E8%A6%81%E5%A0%85%E6%8C%81%E6%88%BF%E4%BD%8F%E4%B8%8D%E7%82%92%E5%AE%9A%E4%BD%8D&d=PGKZrCzpIeFm7bz4D1EKrab0OKgTvMyjK8k7SjVk7cc%3D&h=6f48e055\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.hk01.com/財經快訊/563655/中央經濟工作會議-要堅持房住不炒定位</a>"},{"pid":"5c13ac2dce0c9e3235d4c8f3c256496fd23d4bbb","tid":2330933,"uid":19454,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-18T11:22:03.000Z","msg":"講過幾多次<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7999d9aa37423776f39b0037581d69c0a3dc4665","tid":2330933,"uid":156652,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-18T11:22:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/MNheVoR.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FMNheVoR.gif&h=a24a436c&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"156433ae3566f26a94d1ad159c731aad8be6f82f","tid":2330933,"uid":19454,